      "text": [
        "3535 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلْمَمْلُوكُ إِذَا هَرَبَ وَ لَمْ يَخْرُجْ مِنْ مِصْرِهِ لَمْ يَكُنْ آبِقاً\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3535 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"If a slave runs away but does not leave his city, he is not considered a runaway (abiq).\""
        ]
      }
    }
